Life at Healthy.io

Who are we?

We believe in meaningful work that doesn’t disrupt but makes a difference. With offices in London, Tel Aviv and Boston we are able to see the global impact we have on healthcare, all at the speed of life.

Moving at the speed of life means that wherever our people, users, partners and future employees are, we meet them then and there. We are the technology providing clinical results at life’s critical moments, syncing healthcare with life by transforming the smartphone camera into a medical device.

Join us on our global mission to close the gaps in healthcare and access for all people, at all walks of life.

Our values

Open-minded

We are always willing to listen and learn from the opinions of others.

Bold

We aren't afraid to dream big and try hard.

Expert

We take pride in what we do and aim to be the very best at it.

Accountable

We take ownership of everything we do.

Human

We are 'people people' and expect that from everyone in our team.

What does a Healthy career look like?

We’re looking for creative innovators, who share our passion for bots, AI, and technology who are excited to work for a cause and not just applause. Makers who love to build stuff with their own hands and challenge the status quo.

Welcome to Livi

Join our mission to build better and more accessible healthcare for everyone.

Why join Livi

  • Grow as a leader

    Fast growing companies need fast growing people and great leaders. This is why we are keen to heavily invest in our leaders ability and growth. When you are hired or promoted into a manager role at Kry we will make sure you have the right tools to build and manage your team in the right way. Apart from leadership onboarding and leadership training we now offer a 6 month coaching program.

  • Flexible public holidays

    We all celebrate different things in life and this is also true for holidays. We're happy to say that we have a flexible public holiday policy which gives you as an employee the ability to switch a public holiday for another day off that is more in line with who you are and what you think is important.

  • Stay calm and clear

    We want to provide tools for our people to recharge their batteries, which is why we have meditation and yoga classes every week.
